        </profile>
        <profile name="Processional Shieldwall" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="c391-d25e-49b4-ad70">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While other friendly leader units are within 1” of this unit and this unit is closer or the same distance to an active enemy unit visible to this unit, those leader units gain the following ability:


Guarded: For each wound a model in this unit is selected to suffer, you may roll a D6. On a 5+, that attack fails.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
