          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit is Activated, you may ‘utter its trigger word’. If you do, this unit gains the following abilities: Resilient 6+ Frenzied Berserkers: This unit cannot capture objectives. Disabled Pacifier: Each time this unit makes a move, it must Advance and it must end that move as close as possible to the closest enemy unit. Deadly Cocktail: For each attack this unit makes, a successful Wound Roll for that attack causes an additional wound.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
