        <profile name="Munitorum Cherub" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="7d51-60ea-3739-e8ae">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">Once per battle, after selecting targets for this unit’s weapons, you may ‘use the blessed ammunition’ and select a model in this unit. If you do, for each attack made for the selected model this turn, reroll a failed Hit and Wound roll for that attack. (Use the Cherub models to note when a unit has yet to use this ability and remove them after the ability is used.)</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <constraints>
